{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3",
    "translationId": "rsv",
    "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
    "chapterNumber": 3,
    "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3",
    "summary": "Source text for 1 Chronicles 3 in Revised Standard Version."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.1",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:1",
      "text": "These are the sons of David that were born to him in Hebron: the first-born Amnon, by Ahino-am the Jezreelitess; the second Daniel, by Abigail the Carmelitess,",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.2",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:2",
      "text": "the third Absalom, whose mother was Maacah, the daughter of Talmai, king of Geshur; the fourth Adonijah, whose mother was Haggith;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.3",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:3",
      "text": "the fifth Shephatiah, by Abital; the sixth Ithre-am, by his wife Eglah;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.4",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:4",
      "text": "six were born to him in Hebron, where he reigned for seven years and six months. And he reigned thirty-three years in Jerusalem.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.5",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:5",
      "text": "These were born to him in Jerusalem: Shime-a, Shobab, Nathan, and Solomon, four by Bath-shua, the daughter of Ammiel;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.6",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:6",
      "text": "then Ibhar, Elishama, Eliphelet,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.7",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:7",
      "text": "Nogah, Nepheg, Japhia,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.8",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:8",
      "text": "Elishama, Eliada, and Eliphelet, nine.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.9",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:9",
      "text": "All these were David's sons, besides the sons of the concubines; and Tamar was their sister.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.10",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:10",
      "text": "The descendants of Solomon: Rehoboam, Abijah his son, Asa his son, Jehoshaphat his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.11",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:11",
      "text": "Joram his son, Ahaziah his son, Joash his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.12",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:12",
      "text": "Amaziah his son, Azariah his son, Jotham his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.13",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:13",
      "text": "Ahaz his son, Hezekiah his son, Manasseh his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.14",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:14",
      "text": "Amon his son, Josiah his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.15",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:15",
      "text": "The sons of Josiah: Johanan the first-born, the second Jehoiakim, the third Zedekiah, the fourth Shallum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.16",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:16",
      "text": "The descendants of Jehoiakim: Jeconiah his son, Zedekiah his son;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.17",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:17",
      "text": "and the sons of Jeconiah, the captive: She-alti-el his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.18",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:18",
      "text": "Malchiram, Pedaiah, Shenazzar, Jekamiah, Hoshama, and Nedabiah;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.19",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:19",
      "text": "and the sons of Pedaiah: Zerubbabel and Shime-i; and the sons of Zerubbabel: Meshullam and Hananiah, and Shelomith was their sister;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.20",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:20",
      "text": "and Hashubah, Ohel, Berechiah, Hasadiah, and Jushab-hesed, five.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.21",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:21",
      "text": "The sons of Hananiah: Pelatiah and Jeshaiah, his son Rephaiah, his son Arnan, his son Obadiah, his son Shecaniah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.22",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:22",
      "text": "The sons of Shecaniah: Shemaiah. And the sons of Shemaiah: Hattush, Igal, Bariah, Ne-ariah, and Shaphat, six.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.23",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:23",
      "text": "The sons of Ne-ariah: Eli-o-enai, Hizkiah, and Azrikam, three.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.3.24",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:24",
      "text": "The sons of Eli-o-enai: Hodaviah, Eliashib, Pelaiah, Akkub, Johanan, Delaiah, and Anani, seven.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
